{"tid":902700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社報導，美國國會指責中國放鬆對朝鮮制裁","createTime":"2018-11-15T04:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T04:41:57.000Z","uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"39ccbe653398831b87ea68065cfc3adb51588a86","tid":902700,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T04:12:07.000Z","msg":"按照路透社報導，美中經濟與安全審議委員會（US -China Economic and Security Review Commission)指責中國放寬對朝鮮既制裁，並呼籲財政部於180日內提供中國對朝鮮狀況既報告，包括牽涉與朝鮮進行貿易既中國官員、企業及金融機構名單，以考慮在未來制裁相關人士機構<br />\n<br />\n委員會又指中國響2018年初已經放寬制裁，冇跟足聯合國既制裁指令，更高調進行中朝官方交流、就業及經濟援助<br />\n<br />\n中國外交官楊潔箎在上星期訪美時，指中國「嚴謹執行聯合國既指示」。相反，Trump表示中國因為近期貿易戰，正對朝鮮無核化進度產生負面影響<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-usa-congress/china-appears-to-relax-north-korea-sanctions-report-to-u-s-congress-idUSKCN1NJ387\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-northkorea-usa-congress%2Fchina-appears-to-relax-north-korea-sanctions-report-to-u-s-congress-idUSKCN1NJ387&d=5AQysucJKw%2B06WvvYsRLX0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=5920e0e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-northkorea-usa-congress%2Fchina-appears-to-relax-north-korea-sanctions-report-to-u-s-congress-idUSKCN1NJ387&h=7950a598\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-usa-congress/china-appears-to-relax-north-korea-sanctions-report-to-u-s-congress-idUSKCN1NJ387</a>"},{"pid":"0054e5cf0b7c32ad44247b2e92698e0c52c71ff4","tid":902700,"uid":26329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"人地無諗過要制裁呀 收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b0e67bc281bff97c76a7bd994f13cfa18ed7e7","tid":902700,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}